          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1684417973587-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>charred harissa cabbage </strong>over the<strong> fruity couscous </strong>and drizzle over the <strong>whipped feta sauce</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining chopped parsley </strong>and<strong> sliced chillies </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
